          <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-2">
            <li>• High-impact stages.</li>
            <li>• Live shows with national and international artists.</li>
            <li>• Professional production, lighting and sound.</li>
            <li>• Premium activations for brands and sponsors.</li>
            <li>• Productions that combine music, art and technology to create unique moments.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
