            <li>• Scenography, lighting and special effects.</li>
            <li>• Guest DJs and artists.</li>
            <li>• Interactive experiences and brand activations.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our seal</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Each party has its own DNA, but all share the same spirit: to offer a safe, exclusive and best-energy experience.</p>
        </div>
