            <li>• Professional lighting and special effects (laser, confetti, cold sparks, LED screens).</li>
            <li>• Interactive experiences: photo booths, Cromática MakeUp (Glitter), Glow Beer Pong Championship and exclusive dynamics.</li>
            <li>• Personalized wristbands.</li>
            <li>• Security with OS10 certified guards.</li>
            <li>• Professional photography and after movie.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our seal</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-300">Each PROM is the most important night of your school stage, an experience that combines safety, innovation and premium production, to close your stage with style and celebrate a night that will remain forever in the class's memory.</p>
